
# ArcadeGame

Docs voor onze ArcadeGame.


## Entity

### Component based design:

  * Physics
    * Solid
    * Small (for stuff that should have no real physical influence)
    * Container
  * Life
    * Immutable
    * Alive
  * InterActive
    * Nothing
    * Lethal
  * Printer
    * Simple
    * LifeBased

### Dispatchers used for collisions:
  * Automatically generated code based on toml file.

## Online play
  * HTML: websocket-based local area network online multiplayer support.

## Graphics
  * Provided by Kenney as a free, royalty-free platformer sprites pack.
